<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Bachelor in Paradise Star Jamie Doran has publicly defended Kaitlyn Hoppe after her relationship with Bernard Tomic was exposed. </p>

<p>In a comment made on the So Dramatic Podcast Instagram account on Monday, Jamie, 40, wrote of The Bachelor starlet:  'Probably the biggest heart of gold you'll ever meet in your life. </p>

<p>'She'll be okay. She's got a lot of good people around her who will support her through the many peaks and troughs of reality TV' he added. </p>

<p>Bachelor in Paradise Star Jamie Doran (pictured) has publicly defended Kaitlyn Hoppe after her relationship with Bernard Tomic was exposed</p>

<p>It comes after troubled Australian tennis star Bernard and The Bachelor contestant had a very public row inside strip club last weekend.</p>

<p>Tomic, 27, and Hoppe, 26, were seen arguing inside Hollywood Showgirls strip club during a big night out on the Gold Coast on Saturday, September 5.</p>

<p>The argument led to Ms Hoppe leaving the club, while Tomic - a regular patron - was allowed to stay.</p>

<p>In a comment made on the So Dramatic Podcast Instagram account on Monday, Jamie, 40, wrote of The Bachelor starlet: 'Probably the biggest heart of gold you'll ever meet in your life'</p>

